Mean = 157.6

Sorted list: 124, 132, 134, 140, 146, 166, 174, 178, 182, 200  
Median = average of 5th and 6th: (146 + 166)/2 = 156

So roughly centered around 156–158.

So perhaps they are **even numbers near 160**, excluding some.

